Help on skill: Berserk
Skill type: neutral
Usage duration: 6 rounds
Affecting stats: Str/Con

Berserk increases fighters ability to score hits and it greatly
increases the damage of inflicted hits.
Berserk also gives a strong feeling of invulnerability resulting
in dramatical raise of berserker's constitution and strength.
However, this means that berserking person forgets to dodge.
Parrying is still possible.
As a side effect, a berserker blind of rage picks up fights randomly.
Berserking in combat affects the damage done by skills 'strike' and
'tremendous blow'.
Berserkers cannot be stunned by any amount of pain.

